==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: nuclear war
<hw>nuclear war</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A war in which nuclear weapons
are used by both sides. As generally used, the term assumes major use of
nuclear weapons by at least two opposing warring states. As of 1999, no
nuclear war has occurred.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>nuclear warhead</ent>⟦br⟧
